# EJS / Bootstrap UI Conventions

- Treat `src/templates/` as the source of generated HTML; do not patch generated HTML by hand.
- Prefer Bootstrap 5 cards, buttons, badges, progress bars, grid, and utility classes before adding custom CSS.
- Keep UI structure consistent with existing partials and reusable components such as `modal-base.ejs` and `ability-card.ejs`.
- Maintain responsive layout and accessible labels/ARIA attributes when adding interactive elements.
- Keep template logic small; move complex behavior into TypeScript scene or component code.
